    "Although written in a different way compared to the developer patch, this patch achieves similar effect and passes the developer provided test-suite for this issue.",
    "Program Improvement FrameworkIn this section, we discuss the design of AutoCodeRover.",
    "Au-toCodeRover is a system incorporating AI agents for program improvement tasks in large software projects.",
    "AutoCodeRover is designed to work in a realistic software development lifecycle, in which users submit issue reports to a software repository describing a bug, and the project maintainers craft a patch to resolve the issue.",
    "With a submitted issue, AutoCodeRover autonomously analyzes the submitted issue, retrieves the relevant code context in the software project, and generates a patch."
